                }, this), "Hi\u1EC7n t\u1EA1i, t\xEDnh n\u0103ng h\u1EE7y \u0111\u0103ng k\xFD SEasy Vay Ti\xEAu D\xF9ng v\u1EABn \u0111ang trong qu\xE1 tr\xECnh x\xE2y d\u1EF1ng & ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n. S\u1EBD kh\xF4ng ph\xE1t sinh b\u1EA5t c\u1EE9 kho\u1EA3n ph\xED n\xE0o t\u1EEB SEasy Vay Ti\xEAu D\xF9ng n\u1EBFu Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi d\xF9ng kh\xF4ng c\xF2n d\u01B0 n\u1EE3. Tr\u01B0\u1EDDng h\u1EE3p c\u1EA7n th\xEAm th\xF4ng tin, vui l\xF2ng li\xEAn h\u1EC7 v\u1EDBi B\u1ED9 ph\u1EADn CSKH Shopee \u0111\u1EC3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c h\u1ED7 tr\u1EE3.", /*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("div", {
                  className: classes.headerp,
                  children: "9. N\u1EBFu g\u1EB7p c\xE1c v\u1EA5n \u0111\u1EC1 tr\xEAn trang ch\u1EE7 SEasy Vay Ti\xEAu D\xF9ng, t\xF4i c\u1EA7n l\xE0m g\xEC? "
                }, void 0, false, {
                  fileName: _jsxFileName,
                  lineNumber: 300,
